#: src/changelog.md:815
msgid ""
"Musl and auditwheel compliance: Using the new `musl` feature combined with "
"the musl target, you can build completely static binaries. The `password-"
"storage`, which enables keyring integration, is now disabled by default. The "
"Pypi packages are now statically linked with musl so that they are "
"audtiwheel compliant."
msgstr ""

